Cloud Vision V1 API - Class Google::Cloud::Vision::V1::AsyncBatchAnnotateFilesRequest (v1.16.0)

Reference documentation and code samples for the Cloud Vision V1 API class Google::Cloud::Vision::V1::AsyncBatchAnnotateFilesRequest.

Multiple async file annotation requests are batched into a single service call.
